1
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:27,240
I was also disheartened.

2
00:01:27,960 --> 00:01:28,760
But,

3
00:01:29,680 --> 00:01:31,480
until that day when I drank your cup of

4
00:01:31,480 --> 00:01:33,320
improved Qimen Black Tea,

5
00:01:34,320 --> 00:01:36,360
I once again

6
00:01:36,840 --> 00:01:39,560
saw hope for our Hu family.

7
00:01:44,400 --> 00:01:45,200
Day.

8
00:01:45,200 --> 00:01:47,800
I have brought the Hu family's ancestral seal.

9
00:01:52,920 --> 00:01:54,080
Linglong.

10
00:01:55,560 --> 00:01:57,120
Right now, the Hu family

11
00:01:57,920 --> 00:02:00,120
has reached a critical moment.

12
00:02:00,640 --> 00:02:01,600
We cannot

13
00:02:01,600 --> 00:02:03,460
be without a leader for even a day.

14
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:05,720
The current Hu family

15
00:02:06,120 --> 00:02:07,840
is facing internal and external troubles.

16
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:09,080
Only you

17
00:02:09,560 --> 00:02:11,440
can take on this great responsibility

18
00:02:11,440 --> 00:02:13,640
and succeed as the head of the Hu family.

19
00:02:14,040 --> 00:02:17,280
I hope for the sake of the Hu family's ancestors

20
00:02:18,120 --> 00:02:21,200
and your father's spirit in heaven,

21
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:23,600
you can forget personal grudges,

22
00:02:23,600 --> 00:02:25,260
understand the greater good,

23
00:02:25,720 --> 00:02:27,680
and accept this Hu family seal.

24
00:02:28,160 --> 00:02:30,079
Do not let your father Wenzhong's

25
00:02:30,079 --> 00:02:33,000
years of hard work go to waste.

26
00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:35,560
Linglong,

27
00:02:36,720 --> 00:02:38,000
I

28
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:39,400
beg you.

29
00:02:53,480 --> 00:02:54,280
Mother.

30
00:02:55,040 --> 00:02:57,300
I will be traveling to the West tomorrow,

31
00:02:57,480 --> 00:03:00,920
bringing the Qimen Black Tea to participate in the exposition.

32
00:03:00,920 --> 00:03:03,400
Please bless me so that everything goes smoothly

33
00:03:03,400 --> 00:03:04,730
and my wishes come true.

34
00:03:05,200 --> 00:03:07,860
Let the Qimen Black Tea regain its former glory.

35
00:03:13,120 --> 00:03:16,400
Wish fulfilled, you can return to the present world.

36
00:03:16,960 --> 00:03:17,840
Right.

37
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:19,840
How could I forget about going home?

38
00:03:20,040 --> 00:03:21,640
Since I've already helped Hu Linglong

39
00:03:21,640 --> 00:03:22,480
improve the black tea,

40
00:03:22,480 --> 00:03:24,560
then naturally I can time-travel back.

41
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:26,020
Then what am I waiting for?

42
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:32,880
But if I leave,

43
00:03:33,520 --> 00:03:34,880
what about Linglong?

44
00:03:40,560 --> 00:03:41,440
Zhinian.

45
00:03:41,920 --> 00:03:43,360
You gave me a button as a gift.

46
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:45,600
I will bring it with me across the ocean this time.

47
00:03:45,600 --> 00:03:47,000
When I think of you,

48
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:48,640
it will bring me comfort.

49
00:03:54,880 --> 00:03:55,640
Qiao Xin.

50
00:03:56,440 --> 00:03:57,520
Qiao Xin?

51
00:03:59,480 --> 00:04:02,080
Qiao Xin hasn't spoken for a while.

52
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:04,480
Could she have already returned to heaven?

53
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:06,520
What's wrong?

54
00:04:09,040 --> 00:04:10,240
I thought

55
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:12,720
you had gone back to being an immortal.

56
00:04:12,720 --> 00:04:14,560
I was going to go back.

57
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:15,720
But I thought about it,

58
00:04:15,720 --> 00:04:17,959
I should see this through to the end.

59
00:04:17,959 --> 00:04:18,959
We haven't been to the exposition yet.

60
00:04:18,959 --> 00:04:20,320
How could I leave you alone?

61
00:04:20,320 --> 00:04:20,959
Besides,

62
00:04:20,959 --> 00:04:22,680
you will be unfamiliar with the place and the people there.

63
00:04:22,680 --> 00:04:23,960
I can speak some foreign languages,

64
00:04:23,960 --> 00:04:25,490
and can be your translator.

65
00:04:26,440 --> 00:04:27,280
Qiao Xin,

66
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:29,960
I feel much more at ease with you here.

67
00:04:30,800 --> 00:04:31,640
Rest assured.

68
00:04:39,720 --> 00:04:40,600
No, officer!

69
00:04:41,840 --> 00:04:42,240
No,

70
00:04:42,880 --> 00:04:43,560
officer!

71
00:04:43,840 --> 00:04:44,770
You can't leave!

72
00:04:46,600 --> 00:04:47,800
Hu Wenyi.

73
00:04:49,400 --> 00:04:50,200
Spare my life!

74
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:51,840
I beg you!

75
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:54,080
Tell Mr. Yamamoto,

76
00:04:54,400 --> 00:04:55,080
I can

77
00:04:55,080 --> 00:04:55,880
immediately

78
00:04:55,880 --> 00:04:57,080
give him the black tea recipe.

79
00:04:57,080 --> 00:04:57,600
Really.

80
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:58,560
Take me there now,

81
00:04:58,560 --> 00:05:00,560
and I'll give it to you immediately.

82
00:05:01,520 --> 00:05:02,720
It's too late.

83
00:05:03,320 --> 00:05:05,920
Your son is already waiting for you in hell.

84
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:21,600
Thank you for coming to see me off, Auntie.

85
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:22,560
Linglong.

86
00:05:22,560 --> 00:05:24,960
It's a long journey to the West.

87
00:05:24,960 --> 00:05:26,080
It will be full of hardships.

88
00:05:26,080 --> 00:05:28,440
Take good care of yourself on the way.

89
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:30,440
Rest assured, Auntie.

90
00:05:30,440 --> 00:05:31,920
I will definitely overcome all difficulties

91
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:33,120
and make this trip worthwhile,

92
00:05:33,120 --> 00:05:35,360
making Keemun black tea world-famous.

93
00:05:37,480 --> 00:05:38,520
But about this matter...

94
00:05:38,520 --> 00:05:39,120
Linglong,

95
00:05:39,320 --> 00:05:40,780
I know what you want to say.

96
00:05:41,200 --> 00:05:42,560
We certainly won't

97
00:05:42,560 --> 00:05:44,560
mention this to Zhinian.

98
00:05:45,040 --> 00:05:47,480
You don't want Zhinian to worry about you,

99
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:48,400
right?

100
00:05:50,640 --> 00:05:51,400
Yes.

101
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:53,840
It's time to board the ship.

102
00:05:53,840 --> 00:05:54,520
Go ahead.

103
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:56,440
Take care, Mrs. Xu.

104
00:05:58,720 --> 00:05:59,780
Be careful, Madam.

105
00:06:07,880 --> 00:06:08,880
Hu Linglong,

106
00:06:08,880 --> 00:06:09,520
stop right there!

107
00:06:09,520 --> 00:06:10,240
Who are you?

108
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:12,120
Mr. Yamamoto said

109
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:14,320
you cannot leave Qimen alive today.

110
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:16,840
So you are Yamamoto Toru's dogs.

111
00:06:16,840 --> 00:06:18,370
Go back and tell your master

112
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:20,480
I will settle the score for stealing the Hu family's tea recipe

113
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:21,880
with him sooner or later.

114
00:06:22,160 --> 00:06:23,360
Bastards!

115
00:06:23,360 --> 00:06:24,120
Attack!

116
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:25,880
Watch out, Miss!

117
00:06:26,840 --> 00:06:27,680
Oh no.

118
00:06:27,680 --> 00:06:28,840
Hu Linglong is in danger.

119
00:06:28,840 --> 00:06:29,760
Hu Linglong!

120
00:06:29,760 --> 00:06:30,480
They want to kill you.

121
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:31,440
Run!

122
00:06:33,159 --> 00:06:33,960
Bastards!

123
00:06:33,960 --> 00:06:35,240
Ah!

124
00:06:35,600 --> 00:06:36,560
Miss, run!

125
00:06:36,560 --> 00:06:37,220
Uncle Zhao!

126
00:06:48,360 --> 00:06:49,020
Uncle Zhao!

127
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:50,840
Hu Linglong!

128
00:06:50,840 --> 00:06:51,680
Watch your back!

129
00:06:51,680 --> 00:06:52,360
Watch out!

130
00:06:55,280 --> 00:06:55,920
Madam,

131
00:06:55,920 --> 00:06:57,320
it seems something happened at the pier.

132
00:06:57,320 --> 00:06:58,720
Should we go back and check?

133
00:06:58,720 --> 00:07:00,560
It looks like something did happen.

134
00:07:00,560 --> 00:07:02,360
What can we women do?

135
00:07:02,360 --> 00:07:03,760
Master is patrolling the street ahead.

136
00:07:03,760 --> 00:07:04,760
Let's go find him.

137
00:07:05,040 --> 00:07:05,480
Yes.

138
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:06,010
Let's go.

139
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:14,080
This...

140
00:07:14,080 --> 00:07:15,520
What is going on here?

141
00:07:34,440 --> 00:07:35,320
Catch them!

142
00:07:36,159 --> 00:07:36,880
Run!

143
00:07:37,080 --> 00:07:37,680
Linglong!

144
00:07:38,920 --> 00:07:39,520
Linglong!

145
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:40,520
Linglong!

146
00:07:41,440 --> 00:07:42,040
Linglong!

147
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:43,280
Linglong!

148
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:02,220
Uncle Zhao!

149
00:08:02,960 --> 00:08:03,480
Uncle Zhao!

150
00:08:03,480 --> 00:08:03,960
Sigh...

151
00:08:04,240 --> 00:08:05,800
I've sent someone for a doctor.

152
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:06,800
Go wait at the door quickly.

153
00:08:06,800 --> 00:08:07,400
Okay.

154
00:08:08,560 --> 00:08:09,360
Madam.

155
00:08:10,320 --> 00:08:11,680
I have official business to attend to.

156
00:08:11,680 --> 00:08:12,680
I can't stay long.

157
00:08:13,080 --> 00:08:14,760
Linglong is seriously injured.

158
00:08:14,760 --> 00:08:16,000
So please take good care of her

159
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:17,730
and stay here to look after her.

160
00:08:17,760 --> 00:08:18,240
Hurry.

161
00:08:18,640 --> 00:08:19,320
Doctor!

162
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:20,320
Hurry.

163
00:08:22,240 --> 00:08:23,080
Miss!

164
00:08:23,560 --> 00:08:25,200
You must be okay.

165
00:08:27,880 --> 00:08:28,520
Doctor,

166
00:08:28,920 --> 00:08:30,040
how is

167
00:08:30,200 --> 00:08:31,640
my lady's injury?

168
00:08:31,720 --> 00:08:33,880
I have removed the bullet from her body.

169
00:08:33,880 --> 00:08:35,600
The wound has been properly treated.

170
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:37,679
Although it didn't hit any vital organs,

171
00:08:37,679 --> 00:08:39,640
she is in a coma due to excessive blood loss.

172
00:08:39,640 --> 00:08:41,039
Her fate is in God's hands now.

173
00:08:41,039 --> 00:08:41,919
Thank you, doctor,

174
00:08:41,919 --> 00:08:43,080
for saving my lady.

175
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:44,080
Thank you for your hard work, doctor.

176
00:08:44,080 --> 00:08:45,200
This way.

177
00:08:59,160 --> 00:09:00,040
Mrs. Xu,

178
00:09:00,280 --> 00:09:01,760
thank you for your trouble today.

179
00:09:01,760 --> 00:09:03,040
Please head back now.

180
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:04,000
Right now,

181
00:09:04,160 --> 00:09:06,240
Linglong needs someone by her bedside.

182
00:09:06,240 --> 00:09:07,520
Your foot is injured,

183
00:09:07,760 --> 00:09:09,420
making it hard for you to walk.

184
00:09:09,440 --> 00:09:10,400
For the next few days,

185
00:09:10,400 --> 00:09:11,920
I will come over to see her.

186
00:09:12,560 --> 00:09:13,320
After all,

187
00:09:13,840 --> 00:09:14,880
Linglong's safety

188
00:09:14,880 --> 00:09:16,480
is the most important thing.

189
00:09:16,560 --> 00:09:17,520
On behalf of my lady,

190
00:09:17,520 --> 00:09:18,960
I thank you, Madam.

191
00:09:20,120 --> 00:09:20,680
Alas.

192
00:09:23,200 --> 00:09:23,920
However,

193
00:09:24,880 --> 00:09:26,340
in just a few short months,

194
00:09:26,760 --> 00:09:29,160
her parents passed away one after another,

195
00:09:29,360 --> 00:09:32,020
and she was repeatedly framed by her relatives.

196
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:33,080
Now,

197
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:34,480
she is severely injured

198
00:09:35,080 --> 00:09:36,540
and her life is uncertain.

199
00:09:37,680 --> 00:09:39,720
The suffering Linglong has endured,

200
00:09:39,720 --> 00:09:40,980
if it were anyone else,

201
00:09:41,360 --> 00:09:43,280
who could bear it?

202
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:45,920
It breaks one's heart to see,

203
00:09:46,480 --> 00:09:48,080
and brings tears to one's eyes to hear.

204
00:09:48,080 --> 00:09:49,200
How could I

205
00:09:49,360 --> 00:09:50,960
just stand by and watch?

206
00:09:52,640 --> 00:09:53,360
Uncle Zhao,

207
00:09:53,520 --> 00:09:54,650
go back to your work.

208
00:09:55,960 --> 00:09:56,600
Madam,

209
00:09:56,640 --> 00:09:58,170
thank you for your trouble.

210
00:10:16,960 --> 00:10:17,640
Qiao Xin,

211
00:10:18,120 --> 00:10:19,240
you are still here.

212
00:10:19,800 --> 00:10:21,330
I thought you had gone back.

213
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:22,680
I...

214
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:23,760
No.

215
00:10:23,800 --> 00:10:25,080
I have been here all along.

216
00:10:25,080 --> 00:10:25,800
But...

217
00:10:25,880 --> 00:10:27,340
But how did I end up at home?

218
00:10:27,920 --> 00:10:28,920
I remember

219
00:10:29,240 --> 00:10:30,320
I was at the pier...

220
00:10:31,240 --> 00:10:32,040
Someone...

221
00:10:33,920 --> 00:10:34,760
It's alright now.

222
00:10:34,760 --> 00:10:35,690
Don't be afraid.

223
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:36,640
Linglong,

224
00:10:36,920 --> 00:10:37,440
because

225
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:38,520
I'm leaving soon,

226
00:10:38,720 --> 00:10:41,050
so there are some things I want to tell you.

227
00:10:42,480 --> 00:10:43,640
Actually...

228
00:10:44,160 --> 00:10:44,840
I am not

229
00:10:44,840 --> 00:10:46,080
a god from heaven.

230
00:10:46,360 --> 00:10:47,280
I

231
00:10:47,280 --> 00:10:48,320
came from

232
00:10:48,400 --> 00:10:49,680
a long, long time in the future.

233
00:10:49,680 --> 00:10:50,940
I time-traveled here.

234
00:10:53,120 --> 00:10:54,080
How long?

235
00:10:55,680 --> 00:10:56,520
About

236
00:10:56,520 --> 00:10:57,720
over a hundred years.

237
00:10:58,720 --> 00:11:00,580
Then what is the Qing Dynasty like

238
00:11:00,680 --> 00:11:01,940
after a hundred years?

239
00:11:02,880 --> 00:11:04,680
A hundred years later,

240
00:11:05,600 --> 00:11:07,440
there is no Qing Dynasty anymore.

241
00:11:07,440 --> 00:11:08,960
(After the fall of the Qing Dynasty,)

242
00:11:08,960 --> 00:11:11,120
(we went through the Republic of China and founded New China.)

243
00:11:11,120 --> 00:11:13,040
We also built many tall buildings

244
00:11:13,040 --> 00:11:14,040
and made airplanes.

245
00:11:14,040 --> 00:11:15,800
(We even landed on the moon.)

246
00:11:16,080 --> 00:11:18,200
Every family of ours lives very happily.

247
00:11:18,200 --> 00:11:18,960
Qiao Xin,

248
00:11:19,280 --> 00:11:21,480
I really can't hear what you're saying.

249
00:11:21,480 --> 00:11:22,080
Linglong,

250
00:11:22,160 --> 00:11:23,220
you must remember,

251
00:11:23,520 --> 00:11:24,600
we Chinese people

252
00:11:24,720 --> 00:11:25,760
can only unite as one

253
00:11:25,760 --> 00:11:27,320
to drive away the wolves and tigers,

254
00:11:27,320 --> 00:11:30,380
and protect our Chinese mountains and rivers forever.

255
00:11:31,680 --> 00:11:32,760
Unite as one,

256
00:11:32,920 --> 00:11:34,920
and fight against foreign enemies.

257
00:11:34,920 --> 00:11:36,120
Unite as one,

258
00:11:36,360 --> 00:11:38,360
and fight against foreign enemies.

259
00:11:45,080 --> 00:11:45,800
Qiao Xin!

260
00:11:46,120 --> 00:11:46,920
Qiao Xin!

261
00:11:50,120 --> 00:11:50,920
Long'er,

262
00:11:59,440 --> 00:12:00,200
Long'er.

263
00:12:00,400 --> 00:12:01,240
You're awake.

264
00:12:01,760 --> 00:12:03,620
Are you feeling unwell anywhere?

265
00:12:04,520 --> 00:12:05,120
Mother,

266
00:12:08,360 --> 00:12:09,620
you came back to see me.

267
00:12:09,960 --> 00:12:10,960
Oh,

268
00:12:10,960 --> 00:12:12,240
silly child.

269
00:12:12,360 --> 00:12:13,960
Mother has always been here.

270
00:12:14,440 --> 00:12:15,920
But you've grown up.

271
00:12:15,920 --> 00:12:17,920
We certainly can't be like when you were little,

272
00:12:17,920 --> 00:12:19,240
guarding you

273
00:12:19,240 --> 00:12:20,800
and watching you all the time.

274
00:12:20,800 --> 00:12:22,880
You also have to learn to take good care of yourself.

275
00:12:22,880 --> 00:12:23,560
Got it?

276
00:12:27,680 --> 00:12:28,680
You've slept

277
00:12:28,680 --> 00:12:30,160
for a long time this time.

278
00:12:30,360 --> 00:12:31,680
It's time to get out of bed.

279
00:12:31,680 --> 00:12:32,440
Mother

280
00:12:32,440 --> 00:12:34,920
made your favorite black tea crisp.

281
00:12:35,320 --> 00:12:36,380
I'll get it for you,

282
00:12:36,520 --> 00:12:37,080
okay?
